# Module Map

Update this file whenever modules, folders, or responsibilities change.

| Module | Path | Responsibility | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| App bootstrap | `src/index.js`, `src/App.js` | Root render, global providers, router mount | `Suspense` fallback uses `shared/ui/PageLoader` |
| Routing | `src/routes/AppRoutes.jsx` | Route definitions, lazy page loading, protected route wrapping | Contains public and private routes; private routes wrapped with `ProtectedRoute` |
| Auth guard | `src/components/ProtectedRoute/ProtectedRoute.js` | Route-level auth check for private pages | Uses `AuthContext`; renders `LoginPrompt` when not authenticated |
| Context layer | `src/context/*` | App-wide state for auth, currency, booking payload, modal state | `AuthContextProvider` drives session bootstrap and profile hydration |
| API transport | `src/services/api/httpClient.js` | Axios clients, token persistence/refresh, request helpers | Supports app token profile and legacy token profile |
| Auth API wrappers | `src/api/AuthApi.js`, `src/api/UserAuthApis.js` | Login/signup/OTP/profile/logout endpoints | `UserAuthApis.js` appears legacy while `AuthApi.js` is primary |
| Booking + account API wrappers | `src/api/apiService.js` | Booking creation, payment, complaints, concierge, wallet, custom packages | Large service file with mixed domain responsibilities |
| Homepage data layer | `src/api/homepageApi.js`, `src/hooks/useHomepageData.js` | Featured package fetch and short-lived cache | 5-minute in-memory cache in hook |
| Listing data layer | `src/api/listingApi.js`, `src/features/listing/*` | Listing fetch, filters, sorting, pagination | Query params from router are merged with local filters |
| Package detail domain | `src/pages/PackageDetailPage/*`, `src/features/packageDetail/*` | Package detail fetch and desktop/mobile render blocks | Reads `PackageId` from URL query and fetches package detail |
| Booking domain | `src/features/booking/*`, `src/features/travelersInfo/*`, `src/features/bookingStatus/*` | Traveler grouping, pricing, payload shaping, booking state utilities | Core booking logic in `useBookingLogic` hook |
| User settings area | `src/pages/UserSetting/*`, `src/features/paymentMethods/*`, `src/features/remainingPayment/*` | Authenticated user workflows (bookings, wallet, messages, payment methods, wishlist) | Routed behind `ProtectedRoute` |
| Shared UI and utilities | `src/components/*`, `src/shared/*`, `src/Utilities/*`, `src/styles/*` | Reusable UI, assets, helper functions, styling tokens | Includes `ScrollToTop`, currency utils, asset path helpers |
